🏆 SUCCESS WORD FAMILY

1️⃣ Successful
Basic word – achieving goals.
2️⃣ Accomplished
→ synonym of successful
(Tamil: சாதித்தவர்)
She is an accomplished dancer.
🧠 Trick: Accomplish = complete mission
3️⃣ Achiever
→ synonym group (person who succeeds)
(Tamil: சாதனையாளர்)
He is a high achiever.
4️⃣ Triumphant
→ stronger than successful (big victory)
(Tamil: வெற்றி கொண்ட)
She felt triumphant after the competition.
🧠 Think: Triumph = trophy moment
5️⃣ Victorious
→ synonym of triumphant
(Tamil: வெற்றி பெற்ற)
The team was victorious.
6️⃣ Prosperous
→ success in money/life
(Tamil: வளமான / செழிப்பான)
They live a prosperous life.
7️⃣ Flourishing
→ growing successfully
(Tamil: செழித்து வளர்கிறது)
Her business is flourishing.
🧠 Flower → growing beautifully
8️⃣ Thriving
→ synonym of flourishing
(Tamil: செழித்து வளர்கிறது)
She is thriving in her career.
9️⃣ Distinguished
→ respected and successful
(Tamil: சிறப்புமிக்க)
He is a distinguished professor.
🔟 Illustrious
→ very famous and respected
(Tamil: புகழ்பெற்ற)
She comes from an illustrious family.
🧠 Illuminate → shining with fame
